'''刺馬陸總目'''（[[学名|学名]]：{{lang|la|'''Nematophora'''}}），亦作'''刺馬陸超目'''，是[[倍足綱|倍足綱]]的生物。

==分類==
刺馬陸總目（Nematophora）包括下列四個分類元<ref name="Shear 2011 class.">{{cite journal |last=Shear |first=William A. |title=Class Diplopoda de Blainville in Gervais, 1844. In: Zhang, Z.-Q. (Ed.) Animal biodiversity: An outline of higher-level classification and survey of taxonomic richness |journal=[[Zootaxa|Zootaxa]] |year=2011 |volume=3148 |pages=159–164 |url=http://www.mapress.com/zootaxa/2011/f/zt03148p164.pdf |access-date=2015-12-01 |archive-date=2019-07-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190725010639/https://www.mapress.com/zootaxa/2011/f/zt03148p164.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>：
*[[美肢馬陸目|美肢馬陸目]]（Callipodida <small>Pocock, 1894</small>）：有三個亞目，按Stoev, Sierwald & Billey 2008的編排。
**亞目 [[Callipodidea|Callipodidea]] <small>Pocock, 1894</small> (1 family) 
**亞目 [[Schizopetalidea|Schizopetalidea]] <small>Hoffman, 1973</small> (5 families) 
**亞目 [[Sinocallipodidea|Sinocallipodidea]] <small>Shear, 2000</small> (1 family) <ref name="Shear2000"/>
*[[泡馬陸目|泡馬陸目]]（Chordeumatida <small>Pocock, 1894</small>）：有四個亞目，當中有八個屬在Hoffman (1980)屬於[[地位未定|科地位未定]]<ref name="Hoffman1980">{{cite book |last=Hoffman |first=R.L. |year=1980 |title=Classification of the Diplopoda |publisher=[[自然歴史博物館_(日內瓦)|Muséum d-{’}-Histoire Naturelle]] |location=[[日內瓦|Genève]] ([[瑞士|瑞士]]) |pages=237 pp. }}</ref>，現時按Shear (2000)編排略作修訂<ref name="Shear2000">{{cite journal |last=Shear |first=William A. |year=2000 |title=On the milliped family Heterochordeumatidae, with comments on the higher classification of Order Chordeumatida (Diplopoda) |journal=[[Invertebrate_Taxonomy|Invertebrate Taxonomy]] |issue=14 |pages=363–376 |language=en }}</ref>。
**亞目 [[Chordeumatidea|Chordeumatidea]] <small>Pocock, 1894</small> (1 superfamily) 
**亞目 [[Craspedosomatidea|Craspedosomatidea]] <small>Cook, 1895</small>
**亞目 [[Heterochordeumatidea|Heterochordeumatidea]] <small>Shear, 2000</small> (4 superfamilies)<ref name="Shear2000"/>
**亞目 [[Striariidea|Striariidea]] <small>Cook, 1896</small> (2 superfamilies)
*[[斯特馬陸目|斯特馬陸目]]（Stemmiulida <small>Cook, 1895</small>）
*[[Siphoniulida|Siphoniulida]]目 <small>Cook, 1895</small>：Shear (2011)基於其雄性[[生殖肢|生殖肢]]（gonopods）的結構及「噴絲頭」（spinnerets）的存在而歸入本分類<ref name="Shear 2011 class." />；在這之前，Shelley (2003)將之列於[[蠕形马陆下纲|蠕形马陆下纲]]（Helminthomorpha）之下的地位未定分類<ref name="Shelley2003">{{cite journal |last=Shelley |first=R.M. |year=2003 |title=A revised, annotated, family-level classification of the Diplopoda |journal=[[Arthropoda_Selecta|Arthropoda Selecta]] |issue=11 |pages=187–207 |language=en }}</ref>。

